rows.label: qev092701_MSG0020
rows.name:
Heads up—we just received an urgent request from Grenada GG.
It's direct from their chief engineer.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092701_MSG0030
rows.name:
They're asking us to sniff out a prototype Skell for them.
It went radio silent during a test drive.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092701_MSG0040
rows.name:
Thing is, they sounded pretty desperate.
Said they need professionals—a team who'll get the job done right.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092701_MSG0050
rows.name:
Yep, three guesses whose name popped into my skull.
You're taking the job, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092701_MSG0070
rows.name:
I'll send you the coordinates of the last known location
we got from its tracking beacon. Take a good look at 'em.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092701_MSG0080
rows.name: Y'know, there was a rumor going around...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092701_MSG0090
rows.name:
Some news leaks about a new type of Skell
Grenada had in the works...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092701_MSG0100
rows.name:
Could be our missing mech's one and the same.
That'd sure be something.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092701_MSG0110
rows.name:
If it turns out to be a real smash hit,
be nice if we could add it to our arsenal.[ST:wait ]
